    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Brian Richardson</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:287px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/brianprichardson/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/8/89/BrianRichardson.jpg\" width=\"285\" height=\"285\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:BrianRichardson.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Brian Richardson <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Brian Richardson</b>,<br />\na retired American IT professional <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> holding a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor_of_Science\">B.Sc.</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_science\">Computer Science</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rutgers_University\">Rutgers University</a> in 1978. \nDoing computer chess since 1971, Brian Richardson is author of the private <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible chess engine <a href=\"/Tinker\" title=\"Tinker\">Tinker</a>. More recently, inspired by the <a href=\"/index.php?title=AlphaGo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"AlphaGo (page does not exist)\">AlphaGo</a> and <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero</a> publications along with the open source developments around <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a>, Brian tinkers around with <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural networks</a> and <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">Monte-Carlo tree search</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2003_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2003 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brian_Richardson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2003_...\">2003 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brian_Richardson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2003 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=284689\">Itanium2 Testing Crafty &amp; Tinker Informal Results</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Itanium\" title=\"Itanium\">Itanium</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=350527\">Tinker Scores Re: STATIC EVAL TEST (provisional)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 21, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=357424\">Tinker 64 Bit Speedup (Early Results)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 30, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16002\">BitBoard Tests Magic v Non-Rotated 32 Bits v 64 Bits</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 24, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29689\">Doubled and Backward Pawn Engine \"Definitions\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 07, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brian_Richardson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45158\">Yet Another Testing Question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 15, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58946\">Parallel Search to Fixed Depth</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 17, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66013&amp;start=6\">Re: An AlphaZero inspired project</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2018</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66728&amp;start=4\">Re: Chess reinforcement learning by AlphaGo Zero methods</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 09, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67235&amp;start=10\">Re: MCTS beginner questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67600&amp;start=1\">Re: Egbb dll neural network support</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 30, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Neural Networks</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68248\">cutechess-cli running python engines under win7</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 18, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a>, <a href=\"/Python\" title=\"Python\">Python</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69062\">Play v Lc0 on HGM's Server</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 26, 2018</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brian_Richardson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/brianprichardson/\">Brian Richardson | LinkedIn</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brian_Richardson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/brianprichardson/\">Brian Richardson | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/in/brianprichardson?trk=pub-pbmap\">Brian Richardson | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66728&amp;start=4\">Re: Chess reinforcement learning by AlphaGo Zero methods</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Brian Richardson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\